Makro recently launched its new Cornubia store in Umhlanga, KwaZulu-Natal – opening its doors to thousands of customers. The Cornubia store is the largest in the province and the 22nd Makro store in the country. Following the store’s opening, Makro launched its “Back-to-School” sale – offering a variety of items at discounted prices. This includes a range of tech items and gadgets, the best of which are shown below. Makro’s Back-to-School sale will run from 2-21 April 2019. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-301932" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-1-1.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-1-1.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-1-1-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-1-1-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-301934" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-2-1.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-2-1.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-2-1-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/Makro-2-1-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-301936" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/makro-3.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/makro-3.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/makro-3-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/makro-3-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max